aggeration being due to a misreading of a diacritic mark in an early manuscript. This name was moderately popular in the 16th century, but its use in the English-speaking world today is selective. A more recent influence has been the film actress  Ursula Andress  (  b. 1936  in Switzerland)."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Ursula Frismarsh was born in 1158, in Barnham, Sussex, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of John Freshmarsh. She married Robert Holmes in 1186, in Barnham, Sussex, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 5 sons. She died in 1196, in her hometown, at the age of 38, and was buried in England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1158–1196":"1158–1196","1164–Female":"1164–Surnud","1155–1196":"1155–1196","1176–Male":"1176–Surnud","1180–Male":"1180–Surnud","1181–Male":"1181–Surnud","1183–Male":"1183–Surnud","1186–1227":"1186–1227","1138–Male":"1138–Surnud","abt 1180":"umbes 1180","abt 1181":"umbes 1181","abt 1183":"umbes 1183","1176":"1176","1186":"1186","1164":"1164","1196":"1196","abt 1176":"umbes 1176","1183":"1183","1181":"1181","1180":"1180","1227":"1227","1138":"1138","1158":"1158","1155":"1155","Barnham, Westhampnett, Sussex, England":"Barnham, Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Barnham, West Hampnett, Sussex, England":"Barnham, Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Paul Holm, Yorks., Eng.":"Paul-Holm, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Paul Holm Yorks., Eng.":"Paul-Holm, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1158–1196":"1158–1196","1164–Female":"1164–Kuollut","1155–1196":"1155–1196","1176–Male":"1176–Kuollut","1180–Male":"1180–Kuollut","1181–Male":"1181–Kuollut","1183–Male":"1183–Kuollut","1186–1227":"1186–1227","1138–Male":"1138–Kuollut","abt 1180":"noin 1180","abt 1181":"noin 1181","abt 1183":"noin 1183","1176":"1176","1186":"1186","1164":"1164","1196":"1196","abt 1176":"noin 1176","1183":"1183","1181":"1181","1180":"1180","1227":"1227","1138":"1138","1158":"1158",